sequenceDiagram
    actor Guard as Guard
    participant UI as JavaFX Gate Screen
    participant API as Spring Boot DeviceLogController
    participant Service as DeviceLogService
    participant DAO as DeviceLogDAO / DeviceDAO
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Audit as AuditLogDAO

    Guard->>UI: Search student or serial number
    UI->>API: GET device status/search data
    API->>Service: find device and derived state
    Service->>DAO: query device and latest log/view
    DAO->>DB: SELECT devices + latest device_logs
    DB-->>DAO: Device and derived state
    DAO-->>Service: Result
    Service-->>API: Search result
    API-->>UI: JSON result
    Guard->>UI: Confirm entry
    UI->>API: POST /device-logs event_type=entry
    API->>Service: log entry
    Service->>DAO: insert device_logs row
    DAO->>DB: INSERT device_logs
    DB-->>DAO: Triggers validate approved active and alternation
    Service->>Audit: fn_write_audit_log DEVICE_ENTRY
    Service-->>API: Success or rule error
    API-->>UI: HTTP response
